---
const faqs = [
  {
    q: 'Does Remoji work with our custom emojis or only standard ones?',
    a: "Remoji works exclusively with your workspace's custom emojis — both as input and results. It's designed to surface the emojis your team has actually added, not generic ones everyone already knows.",
  },
  {
    q: 'How long does setup take?',
    a: "The install takes under a minute. After that, Remoji processes your emoji library in the background — no action needed from you or your team. Processing time depends on your library size, but everything happens automatically.",
  },
  {
    q: 'What Slack permissions does Remoji need?',
    a: 'Remoji only requests the permissions it needs to read your workspace\'s emoji list and respond to the /remoji slash command. It cannot read messages or access channels.',
  },
  {
    q: 'How much does it cost?',
    a: 'Plans are based on the size of your custom emoji library, not per seat. Free covers up to 500 emojis, Pro up to 5,000, and Business is unlimited.',
  },
  {
    q: 'How do we manage billing?',
    a: 'Admins can upgrade, downgrade, or cancel in the Slack App Home tab through a secure billing portal.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Do you store our emoji images?',
    a: 'Remoji stores descriptions, tags, and visual data about your emojis so it can find similar ones — not the images themselves. This data is tied to your workspace and is never shared.',
  },
  {
    q: 'What if our workspace adds new emojis later?',
    a: 'Remoji automatically detects when new emojis are added to your workspace and processes them in the background.',
  },
];
---

<section id="faq" class="py-24 px-6 border-t border-white/10">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-up">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-semibold text-white sm:text-4xl">Common questions</h2>
    </div>

    <dl class="space-y-4">
      {faqs.map((faq, i) => (
        <details
          class="fade-up group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] overflow-hidden"
          style={`transition-delay: ${i * 60}ms`}
        >
          <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between gap-4 px-5 py-4 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-white/[0.03] transition-colors list-none">
            {faq.q}
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 text-slate-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
                <path d="M4 6l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-5 pb-4 text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed border-t border-white/10 pt-4">
            {faq.a}
          </div>
        </details>
      ))}
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>
